name: COOL
description: COOL is a community-driven digital asset that rewards authentic engagement and creative contribution. Built with deflationary tokenomics and cross-platform utility, COOL empowers holders with governance rights while generating sustainable rewards through staking. More than just a token, COOL represents a movement toward collaborative value creation where creativity, authenticity, and community participation are valued and rewarded in a decentralized ecosystem.
